%N A395710 Expansion of g^6*(6*g-5)/(5-4*g)^4, where g = 1+x*g^5 is the g.f. of A002294.
%F A395710 a(n) = (n+1) * A386566(n+1).
%F A395710 G.f.: (Sum_{k>=0} (10*k+3)/(5*k+3) * binomial(5*k+3,k) * x^k) * (Sum_{k>=0} binomial(5*k,k) * x^k)^3.
%F A395710 Sum_{k>=1} a(k-1) * x^k/k^2 = (1/4) * log( Sum_{k>=0} binomial(5*k-1,k) * x^k ).
%F A395710 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} binomial(5*k+4+l,k) * binomial(5*n-5*k-l,n-k) for every real number l.
%F A395710 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 4^(n-k) * binomial(5*n+5,k).
%F A395710 a(n) = (n+1) * Sum_{k=0..n} 5^(n-k) * binomial(4*n+k+4,k).
%o A395710 (PARI) a(n) = (n+1)*sum(k=0, n, 4^(n-k)*binomial(5*n+5, k));
%Y A395710 Cf. A033504, A395708, A395709, A395711.
